# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# 🎯 Pal.DDD .gitignore — 全面覆盖 .NET + AOT + IDE + CI
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

## ── .NET 构建产物 ──
bin/
obj/
*.nupkg
*.snupkg
*.nuget.props
*.nuget.targets
**/packages/

## ── Native AOT / 发布产物 ──
**/publish/
*.aotprofile
*.aotdetails

## ── IDE / 编辑器 ──
.vs/
.idea/
*.user
*.suo
*.userosscache
*.userprefs
*.csproj.user
*.DotSettings
*.DotSettings.user
*sln.docstates
~$*

## ── 测试 / 覆盖率 ──
**/TestResults/
test-results/
*.coverage
*.coveragexml
*.opencover.xml
BenchmarkDotNet.Artifacts/
**/BenchmarkDotNet.Artifacts/

## ── 诊断 / 日志 ──
*.log
*.etl
*.etw
*.heapsnapshot
*.diagsession
*.trace
**/TraceResults/

## ── OS 元数据 ──
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
Desktop.ini
ehthumbs.db
*.lnk

## ── AI 工具产物（不入库）──
.serena/
.claude/
.codex/
.githooks/
repomix-output.md
**/repomix-output.md
tmp/
/.ai
/.agents
.depwire/
.zcode/

## ── 编辑器临时文件 ──
*~
*.swp
*.swo
*.bak
*.tmp
# Cortex MCP metadata
.cortex/
nul
test-file.txt
stryker-config.json
